Domestic transactions
	695 - Transactions without the flow of funds
		A - Foreign exchange transfer between different customers (including repayment, donation, borrowing, and investment)
		B - Fundings and repayments of short-term foreign exchange loans of domestic banks
		C - Deposit lodgements or deposit repayments of foreign exchange transactions
		D - Realized gain or loss on foreign exchange transactions
		E - Interest payments and receipts from foreign exchange loans
		F - Fundings and repayments of domestic banks medium and long-term foreign exchange loans
		G - Unrealized gain or loss on valuation
		R - Domestic loans receipts between customers
		S - Foreign currency insurance, funds, bonds, and investment related receipts (including interest accrued)
		T - Domestic allowances for family or relatives, donations and inheritance expenditures and receipts
		L - Foreign currency loans receipts between customers
		P - Domestic service receipts between customers
		X - SWAP between NTD and foreign currency
		Y - CCS between NTD and foreign currency
		N - Domestic transaction receipts other than those described above ( i.e. spot transaction settlements,customer's handling fees, and receipts and expenditures of tax)
		Z - The same customer's foreign currency funds change engaged in overseas transaction expenditures and receipts
		Deposit into foreign currency deposit account, Withdrawal from foreign currency deposit account
